review: My 25lb dog was the second smallest dog when we visited and he loves to run. The park is approximately â€Ž100' x 100' with 2 entrances - both are double gated to make sure no dogs slip out. I didn't see a water slide but there is running water and some small pools and bowls that visitors seem to take turns rinsing out and re filling. The dogs all ran and wrestled until they were tired.
